        "Sharpe최적":  f"상관관계를 고려한 최대 샤프 비율 포트폴리오 ({sharpe_desc}). 각 자산 5~65% 제약.",
    }

    mode_tabs = []
    mode_contents = []
    for i, (mode_name, weights) in enumerate(weight_modes.items()):
        active = "active" if i == 0 else ""
        mode_tabs.append(
            f"<button class='mode-btn {active}' "
            f"onclick=\"switchMode('{mode_name}', this)\">{mode_name}</button>"
        )

        # 파이 차트
        labels = [s for s in weights.index if weights[s] > 0]
        values = [weights[s] for s in labels]
        pie_colors = [STYLE_COLORS.get(s, "#aaa") for s in labels]

        fig = go.Figure(go.Pie(
            labels=labels, values=values,
            marker=dict(colors=pie_colors, line=dict(color="#111", width=2)),
            texttemplate="%{label}<br><b>%{value:.1f}%</b>",
            textfont=dict(size=13, family="Malgun Gothic"),
            hovertemplate="%{label}: %{value:.1f}%<extra></extra>",
            hole=0.38,
        ))
        fig.update_layout(
            template="plotly_dark", paper_bgcolor="#111111", plot_bgcolor="#111111",
            margin=dict(l=10, r=10, t=20, b=20), height=300, width=300,
            showlegend=False, autosize=False,
            font=dict(family="Malgun Gothic"),
        )
        cfg = {"displayModeBar": False, "responsive": False}
        pie_html = fig.to_html(full_html=False, include_plotlyjs=False, config=cfg)

        # ETF 매핑 테이블
        th = "padding:7px 10px;font-size:12px;border-bottom:2px solid #2c3e50;text-align:left;"
